Born in 1994, she had a boyish face and was adept and methodical in her work. This year, the 10th day of the first lunar month, was originally her engagement day, in order to fight against the epidemic, Lin haiyue postponed the engagement. On the eve of Valentine's Day, Lin Haiyue in Wuhan, Hubei Province, smiled when she was mentioned as her boyfriend!

January 24 at 4:00 am, has been in the infectious department fever clinic work Lin Haiyue received a call to support Wuhan. Too late to say sorry to her boyfriend and family, she resolutely into the "war epidemic. ".

Luo Xuefeng, her boyfriend, understood. He said goodbye to Lin Haiyue, "I support you in whatever decision you make, and when you return from the epidemic, I am proud of you. "

"In the year of SARS, even though I was only 9 years old, I was always touched by the figure of an angel in White, " Lin said, adding that this was also the impetus for her to take up the nursing post. Although she was an ordinary nurse, she would do her best, to protect the people you can protect.

In order to reduce the risk of virus infection, easy to wear off protective clothing, love the United States arrived in Wuhan, Lin Haiyue cut off long hair. After struggling to shave her head, she gave up the idea and quipped, "I have a big face and all my hair is too ugly, so I secretly pushed it all away. "

Remove the "red makeup" , cut off long hair, postponed the engagement, the reverse and go to Wuhan. Lin Haiyue put on protective clothing and walked into the hospital infection area. Together with his colleagues, he and his colleagues fought against the "epidemic" front line. Every day, he asked and recorded the patients' fever, inhalation, diet and other data. He also gave the patients basic care, transfusion, blood glucose and blood gas, also, keep a record of what everyone needs to be aware of in order to encourage patients to fight the disease. Lin Haiyue always thinks he can do more.

The patient said she could not see Lin's face in full armor, but Lin's voice gave her great confidence. Lin hai-yue said that at that moment, her heart is warm. Fighting in the prevention and control of the epidemic in the first line, do what you should do, every ordinary words can give confidence and strength.

"Although the engagement has been postponed, happiness has not. " Before Valentine's Day, when mentioned boyfriend Luo Xuefeng, lin Haiyue said with a smile, "we won the battle, and there are many good days ahead. Now I want to call my boyfriend Luo Xuefeng and get engaged when I get back. "
